css / javascript: ‘/u03c0’;<br />
linux keyboard: <code class="highlighter-rouge">left-ctrl</code> + <code class="highlighter-rouge">shift</code> + <code class="highlighter-rouge">u</code> után “03c0”.</p>
</blockquote>

